column6: Tips & Tricks from a Noob Pally
Fashion > All, make sure you have good NX before buying gear
Get triple pets and scroll their gear for speed/jump!
An okay HTP can last you for quite a while - worth picking up while you work on getting a 5+ atk MON
No need to wash on warrior! Plenty of base HP, and zhelm + HTP should provide you with some extra MP to wash out if you want
If your party makes fun of your damage, remind them that Crushed Skulls come from the skulls of your enemies
Keep some safety charms for whenever you forget that mounting dispells Power Guard
Don't leech 125-135, join CWKPQ (if only for exp) and get nearly a level per run
